A. Write the names of places in the blanks.
 1. We ran inside the ____________________. (house, hark)
 2. Let us go to ____________________. (church, branch)
 3. Mother is in the ____________________. (over , kitchen)
 4. We are at ____________________. (spoon, school)
 5. There is a boat in the ____________________. (lake, bake)
 6. Many people live in ____________________. (India, ink)
 7. He lives in ____________________. (Mumbai, May)
 8. I clean the ____________________. (room, morn)
B. Fill in the blanks by choosing the correct names from the brackets.
 1. We ﬁnd ____________ in the nest. (birds, ﬁshes)
 2. We ﬁnd ____________ in the ocean. (whales, insects)
 3. We ﬁnd ____________ in the kennel. (dogs, mouse)
 4. We ﬁnd ____________ in the jungle. (lions, dolphins)
 5. We ﬁnd ____________ in the burrow . (rabbits, cats)
